TEXT -800 -80 Left 2 ;This signal is a 1KHz PWM which varies\naccording to state of charging and current limit.\nFor state of charging, the Von of PULSE changes-\n12V DC when vehicle is not connected to EVSE\n9V PWM when vehicle gets connected to EVSE,\n6V PWM when vehicle starts to charge,\n3V DC when vehicle requires ventilation(rare)\nand 0V when there is a fault
